author: Stephanie Anderson
title: Live: Labor criticises Human Services after personal info released
text:
By political reporter Stephanie Anderson Updated February 28, 2017 08:22:21 
Labor MP Linda Burney has criticised the Department of Human Services after personal information was released to "correct the record" over the Centrelink debt recovery debate . 
Elsewhere, changes to the Racial Discrimination Act are expected to be proposed today as the debate about freedom of speech continues. 
Follow live.
